      "span_text": "Little research has investigated the effects of form-focused instruction (FFI) on young second language learners' acquisition of grammar (Bouffard & Sarkar, 2008) . For example, only 21% of the 77 studies of form-focused instruction included in [CITATION_1] often-cited meta-analysis involved children."
